-- Shui On Land Buys Residential Site in Hongqiao, Shanghai for $477 Million
-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 2010-09-30T12:26:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-30/shui-on-land-buys-residential-site-in-hongqiao-shanghai-for-477-million.html
Shui On Land Ltd . agreed to buy
land in Shanghai’s Hongqiao district from the city’s real-estate
trading center for 3.19 billion yuan ($477 million) and will
build a 233,140-square-meter mixed-use development on the site,
according to a filing to Hong Kong’s stock exchange today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  